38:38.233 --> 38:39.534
Matt!

38:40.336 --> 38:41.803
Mr. Matt is not here.

38:41.837 --> 38:43.037
Matt!

38:52.047 --> 38:53.081
Where's your phone?

38:53.115 --> 38:54.415
