39:05.027 --> 39:08.429
Hello. Mr. Matt, there's--

39:08.464 --> 39:10.965
Matt, it's Kevin Garvey.
Is my father with you?

39:11.000 --> 39:12.934
Uh, Kevin, I--no.

39:12.968 --> 39:14.335
What makes you think so?

39:14.370 --> 39:18.006
I think so because he was
just in my fucking backyard

39:18.073 --> 39:19.474
digging up a jar full of cash

39:19.508 --> 39:22.243
with one of your goddamn fliers in it!

39:23.379 --> 39:24.379
Kevin, I--

39:24.413 --> 39:26.714
is he with you or not?

39:29.618 --> 39:32.553
He's almost ready to see you, but...

39:32.588 --> 39:34.629
We need to get something first.

39:35.190 --> 39:36.991
No. You're not getting shit,

39:37.026 --> 39:40.581
not until you tell me where
you are, right fucking now.

39:41.130 --> 39:43.898
Meet us at Sonny's off
route 17, 90 minutes.

39:43.932 --> 39:45.900
Matt...

39:45.934 --> 39:47.301
Matt!

39:47.336 --> 39:49.137
Motherfucker!

40:13.962 --> 40:17.293
Jesus. You were there
the night of the raid.

40:17.566 --> 40:19.500
Yeah, I was there.

40:19.535 --> 40:23.504
Fuck. So many people. I'm sorry
I didn't recognize you, man.

40:23.539 --> 40:25.801
- How did you get out?
- One of the tunnels.

40:26.141 --> 40:28.437
Wayne met up with us at
this fucking rest stop,

40:28.462 --> 40:31.212
gave us some cash, a phone,

40:31.246 --> 40:32.447
looked at me, and then said,

40:32.481 --> 40:34.215
"This girl...

40:34.249 --> 40:38.052
She's everything, yes?"

40:38.087 --> 40:39.887
Motherfucker.

40:39.922 --> 40:41.589
Word for word, man.

40:41.623 --> 40:43.254
Which one?

40:43.459 --> 40:44.559
What?

40:44.593 --> 40:47.729
Which girl? Who are you with?

40:47.763 --> 40:49.137
Christine.

40:49.932 --> 40:51.599
Is she pregnant?

40:52.935 --> 40:55.509
And the baby is Wayne's?

40:56.038 --> 40:57.339
It's not mine.

41:01.443 --> 41:03.377
How many others do you think he's got?

41:03.412 --> 41:04.746
Does it matter?

41:18.761 --> 41:20.428
Did he ever hug you, man?

41:20.959 --> 41:22.468
No.

41:22.598 --> 41:24.226
'Cause he did it to me,

41:24.800 --> 41:28.369
and it was... It was so fucking real, man.

41:31.974 --> 41:33.946
He took away all my pain.

41:40.048 --> 41:41.082
There's got to be a reason

41:41.116 --> 41:43.459
he didn't tell us about each other.

41:44.386 --> 41:45.453
He's got to have a plan.

41:45.487 --> 41:46.854
There's no fucking plan, dude.

41:49.161 --> 41:50.170
Jesus! Jesus Christ!

41:50.246 --> 41:52.460
- Wayne, Wayne, where is that whore?!
- Jesus Christ!

41:54.696 --> 41:55.963
Aah! Fuck!

41:55.998 --> 41:57.565
My baby!

41:57.599 --> 41:58.900
Goddamn it!

41:58.934 --> 42:01.435
He said it would be my baby!

42:01.470 --> 42:03.237
He promised me.

42:03.272 --> 42:06.040
He's the one. He's the only one!

42:06.074 --> 42:07.809
He's the bridge!

42:11.213 --> 42:12.580
Shh. Shh.

42:12.614 --> 42:14.282
He's the one.

42:37.172 --> 42:40.408
They just got here. Want us to grab them?

42:40.442 --> 42:41.475
No. Let them come in.

42:41.510 --> 42:42.844
Copy that.

42:54.523 --> 42:56.041
Kevin.

42:56.959 --> 43:00.228
Reverend, could you give
us a few minutes, please?

43:00.262 --> 43:01.662
I'll be at the counter.

43:01.697 --> 43:03.297
Thank you.

43:04.900 --> 43:06.893
Picked your favorite place.

43:07.736 --> 43:09.919
The only way I could
get you to go to church

43:09.944 --> 43:12.039
was promise you fries and a shake.

43:16.111 --> 43:18.326
Will you please take these off?

43:18.413 --> 43:19.714
No.

43:19.748 --> 43:21.030
Come on.

43:21.055 --> 43:23.684
I saw two units in the parking lot.

43:23.719 --> 43:27.622
I hired that fat-ass 3
booths back. I won't run.

43:28.891 --> 43:30.558
You have my word.

43:34.396 --> 43:35.696
Come on.

43:59.554 --> 44:01.188
What's this?

44:03.825 --> 44:05.159
Son, you need to know,

44:05.193 --> 44:07.795
I wanted to keep you out of this.

44:07.829 --> 44:10.809
I tried to change their minds,

44:11.033 --> 44:13.034
but they wouldn't stop.

44:14.436 --> 44:16.404
They would never stop.

44:21.877 --> 44:23.645
I couldn't find it in the library,

44:23.670 --> 44:27.407
so I had to go to some asshole
in Gabota that sells them.

44:27.482 --> 44:32.720
May 1972. They were very specific.

44:33.689 --> 44:35.122
It had to be this one.

44:42.931 --> 44:45.232
What am I supposed to do with this?

44:45.267 --> 44:47.253
I need you to take it.

44:47.836 --> 44:49.290
Why?

44:49.805 --> 44:51.865
Please, Kevin. Just take--

44:52.007 --> 44:54.775
What fucking difference does it make, huh?

44:57.479 --> 44:59.513
Oh, God.

45:02.451 --> 45:05.553
You need to accept it.

45:05.587 --> 45:07.755
Dad, what does that even mean?

45:10.892 --> 45:13.739
I know you think I'm fucking crazy,

45:14.596 --> 45:16.197
but I'm not.

45:16.231 --> 45:17.898
I'm not, Kevin.

45:17.933 --> 45:23.270
What I hear-- what they say--

45:23.305 --> 45:26.098
it is the goddamn truth.

45:26.308 --> 45:28.171
It's the truth, son.

45:30.645 --> 45:32.213
They don't tell me what they don't--

45:32.247 --> 45:35.514
Oh, Jesus Christ.

45:36.585 --> 45:39.977
I'm trying. This isn't easy.

45:40.822 --> 45:43.457
Ok. I'll--I'll tell him.

45:47.162 --> 45:50.001
Listen to me. Just listen to me.

45:51.600 --> 45:53.426
The lucky ones...

45:54.936 --> 45:56.548
They're not needed.

45:56.805 --> 46:00.088
They get to stay sane.

46:01.109 --> 46:02.643
But we...

46:05.714 --> 46:08.549
We're in the fucking
game now, you understand?

46:08.583 --> 46:11.018
That whistle blew 3 years ago,

46:11.053 --> 46:14.439
and you cannot ignore it anymore.

46:14.990 --> 46:17.324
Your services are being requested.

46:17.359 --> 46:19.835
Eyes open, wide awake.

46:21.196 --> 46:23.230
This is your invitation.

46:24.433 --> 46:25.933
This is your purpose.

46:25.967 --> 46:28.803
This is what you fucking accept.

46:31.239 --> 46:33.779
