47:04.539 --> 47:08.583
I don't accept your bullshit.

47:09.377 --> 47:12.213
I have responsibilities. I have...

47:12.247 --> 47:14.070
Commitments.

47:15.150 --> 47:17.451
I'm not gonna leave my family.

47:20.722 --> 47:22.123
Uh!

47:24.126 --> 47:25.226
You know.

47:25.260 --> 47:28.295
Inside you, you know this is real,

47:28.330 --> 47:30.364
and that makes you a coward.

47:30.398 --> 47:32.733
- A coward?
- You don't want it,

47:32.767 --> 47:34.969
you don't want what I have,

47:35.534 --> 47:36.801
then I relieve you of it.

47:36.888 --> 47:37.922
Sit down.

47:37.947 --> 47:39.707
- I relieve you.
- Dad, calm down.

47:39.741 --> 47:43.043
Just don't wake up. Just stay asleep.

47:43.078 --> 47:45.179
Just go back to sleep.

47:45.213 --> 47:47.982
Don't wake up. Don't anybody wake up!

47:48.016 --> 47:51.285
Go to sleep! Go back to fucking sleep!

49:09.197 --> 49:11.031
You'll come see me on Sunday?

49:11.066 --> 49:12.499
Of course.

49:22.677 --> 49:25.512
They're not gonna let
you off that easy, son.

50:01.049 --> 50:02.483
What?

50:02.517 --> 50:05.519
"Said the father, my dear son,

50:05.553 --> 50:07.755
"relate not thy vision to thy brothers,

50:07.789 --> 50:09.785
lest they concoct a plot against..."

50:09.810 --> 50:11.544
Fuck you, Matt.

50:51.266 --> 50:52.733
Hi.

50:52.767 --> 50:54.368
Hey.

52:36.194 --> 52:38.450
_

